-- Suedzucker May Raise Dividend If Goal Is Met, Platow Brief Says
-- B y   R i c h a r d   W e i s s
-- 2012-01-12T19:26:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-12/suedzucker-may-raise-dividend-if-goal-is-met-platow-brief-says.html
Suedzucker AG may raise its dividend
if its financial goal for operating profit of about 750 million
euros ($962 million) is met,  Platow Brief  said, citing comments
Chief Financial Officer Thomas Koelbl made to analysts.  To contact the reporter on this story:
